item.description:
@X-J-K-X wrote:

cheezscape server on 0.0.0.0:43594

That means your server is online… You can log onto it… The owner, which is you… You log onto server ip: 0.0.0.0 port 43594…

Other people log onto your server using the server IP you have in your no-ip.DUC… As for your compiler, i suggest checking your paths, or using a differen’t one
